{
  "texts": [
    "The holographically dual geometries are identified with the orbifold bagpipe geometries.",
    "In section 3 we compute the half-indices of half-BPS boundary conditions and interfaces in orthogonal and symplectic gauge theories to find the matching pairs for the S-dual configurations.",
    "In section 4 we analyze the large N limits of the half-indices and the giant graviton expansions of the half-indices.",
    "In appendix A we show the q-series expansions of the half-indices.",
    "We have confirmed the matching pairs of half-indices at least up to the terms with q 5 apart from the cases indicated in the tables."
  ]
}